PLOT

Housefull is a romantic comedy entertainer which narrates the story of 
Aarush - the world's unluckiest man. Being jinxed, he believes his bad 
luck can vanish if he finds true love. In this quest for true love how 
one lie leads to another and how different people from different walks 
of life come together adding even more confusion to this hilarious 
comedy of errors resulting in total chaos and mayhem forms the crux of 
the story. The line which Deepika tells Akshay in the film "Jis jhooth 
se kissi ka ghar basta ho, voh jhooth jhooth nahin hota", pretty much
